Release Notes for Version 3.14.2
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.14.2 is the 3rd release in
the Errata Tool 3.14 development period. It closes [12 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes new HTTP APIs for RHN channels and
comments, allows to specify an e-mail for Kerberos principals, has workflow
improvements for rpm-based container advisories and many more improvements.

